OL,3,CEdinburgh Airport evacuated after
OL,4,C'suspicious package' found
OL,6,FPassengers are facing disruption at
OL,7,FEdinburgh Airport after the terminal
OL,8,Fbuilding was evacuated because of a
OL,9,Fsecurity alert.
OL,11,FPolice Scotland said an explosive
OL,12,Fordnance disposal team is at the
OL,13,Fairport and a cordon is in place with
OL,14,Froads closed.
OL,16,F"Edinburgh Airport has been evacuated
OL,17,Fas a precaution following a report of
OL,18,Fa potentially suspicious package,
OL,19,Freported around 6.50pm on Friday," a
OL,20,Fpost on the Police Scotland Edinburgh
OL,21,FFacebook page said.
