OL,3,CEdinburgh Airport evacuated after
OL,4,C'suspicious package' found
OL,6,F"Explosive Ordnance Disposal (EOD) are
OL,7,Fin attendance and a cordon is in place
OL,8,Faround the airport with road closures
OL,9,Fin place."
