OL,3,CEdinburgh Airport evacuated after
OL,4,C'suspicious package' found
OL,6,FScottish Fire and Rescue confirmed
OL,7,Fthere is an ongoing incident and are
OL,8,Fin attendance at Edinburgh Airport.
OL,10,FAn Edinburgh Airport Facebook post
OL,11,Fsaid: "Due to reports of a potentially
OL,12,Fsuspicious item, the airport has been
OL,13,Fevacuated while specialist teams
OL,14,Finvestigate.
OL,16,F"Updates will be issued when
OL,17,Favailable. Passengers should check
OL,18,Fwith their airline for the latest
OL,19,Finformation on their flight."
